"四川内江资中县发生 4.4 级地震，8 天发生 20 起地震，为何会如此频繁地震？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "中国地震台网正式测定：4 月 17 日 6 时 22 分，在四川内江市资中县（北纬 29.65 度，东经 104.86 度）发生 4.4 级地震，震源深度 7 千米。 更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端 根据中国地震台网中心的历史记录显示，从 4 月 10 日到上游新闻发稿前，四川省内江市资中县境内在七天的时间里发生了 19 次地震，最大震级达到 4.2 级。 对此，许多网友表示担心：为什么会连续发生这么多起地震？这是否为大震来临的先兆？四川内江资中 7 天发生 19 起地震，专家回应"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1ca33f46a25cd551410300ba1f31c551_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2028380355976065080"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI7sKFkYfl7rtXEAMaCTExOTE3MjgzNCDK7IXPBjAAOCtAHXITMjAyODM4MDM1NTk3NjA2NTA4MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1989780245977532317", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3ITMTk4OTc4MDI0NTk3NzUzMjMxN3gA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}